OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784715503
OL,3,CAmit Bhatia consortium expresses
OL,4,Cinterest in buying minority stake in
OL,5,CLiverpool
OL,7,FAn investment consortium led by
OL,8,FBritish-Indian millionaire and former
OL,9,FQPR co-owner Amit Bhatia has expressed
OL,10,Fan interest in acquiring a minority
OL,11,Fstake in Liverpool.
OL,13,FLiverpool owners Fenway Sports Group
OL,14,Facknowledged the approach on the same
OL,15,Fday that Bhatia stepped down from the
OL,16,Fboard at QPR to end an 18-year
OL,17,Fassociation, having agreed to transfer
OL,18,Fhis stake in the club to majority
OL,19,Fowner Ruben Gnanalingam.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
