FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784715503
OL,3,CAmit Bhatia consortium expresses
OL,4,Cinterest in buying minority stake in
OL,5,CLiverpool
OL,7,FA spokesperson for FSG said: "An
OL,8,Finvestment consortium led, managed,
OL,9,Fand represented by Amit Bhatia has
OL,10,Fexpressed interest in making a
OL,11,Fstrategic minority investment in
OL,12,FLiverpool Football Club."
OL,14,FNo deal has been agreed with
OL,15,Fdiscussions at an early stage.
OL,17,FIn 2023, FSG sold a minority stake in
OL,18,FLiverpool to investment firm Dynasty
OL,19,Fand any deal with Bhatia, should it
OL,20,Fproceed, is expected to be along
OL,21,Fsimilar lines.
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@YO]
