OL,3,CAmit Bhatia consortium expresses
OL,4,Cinterest in buying minority stake in
OL,5,CLiverpool
OL,7,FFSG, which also owns the Boston Red
OL,8,FSox and the Pittsburgh Penguins,
OL,9,Fbought Liverpool in 2010 for
OL,10,F#300million. Forbes recently valued
OL,11,Fthe club at #4.6billion.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Bhatia announced he was
OL,14,Fleaving his role at QPR. He served as
OL,15,Fvice-chairman before becoming chairman
OL,16,Fin 2018, a role he held for five years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
