PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784715503
OL,3,CAmit Bhatia consortium expresses
OL,4,Cinterest in buying minority stake in
OL,5,CLiverpool
OL,7,FIn quotes on the QPR website, the 46-
OL,8,Fyear-old said: "Since joining the club
OL,9,Fin 2007, QPR has been a deeply
OL,10,Fimportant part of my life and of my
OL,11,Ffamily's life.
OL,13,F"Over nearly two decades we have
OL,14,Fshared promotions, relegations,
OL,15,Funforgettable highs and painful lows,
OL,16,Fand the memories we have made at
OL,17,FLoftus Road alongside the supporters
OL,18,Fwill stay with us forever.
OL,26,@pD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
