FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784715503
OL,3,CAmit Bhatia consortium expresses
OL,4,Cinterest in buying minority stake in
OL,5,CLiverpool
OL,7,F"I step back from my formal
OL,8,Fresponsibilities with pride, gratitude
OL,9,Fand affection. I want to thank the
OL,10,Fplayers, managers, staff, the
OL,11,Fcommunity trust, my fellow board
OL,12,Fmembers and, above all, the fans, who
OL,13,Fhave made me and my family feel part
OL,14,Fof the QPR family for so many years."
OL,16,FBhatia is the son-in-law of Lakshimi
OL,17,FMittal, executive of steel and mining
OL,18,Fcompany ArcelorMittal. Forbes has
OL,19,Frecently valued Mittal's fortune at
OL,20,F#23.2billion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@eO]
